<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NewSouth Technologies — Proposal Template</title>
    <style>
        /* ===== RESET & BASE ===== */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        @page {
            size: letter;
            margin: 0.75in 1in 1in 1in;
        }

        html {
            font-size: 11pt;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background: #fff;
        }

        /* ===== SHARED HEADER (non-cover pages) ===== */
        .page-header {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 8pt;
            color: #999;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .page-header .ph-left {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a2332;
        }

        .page-footer {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 8pt;
            color: #999;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 6px;
            margin-top: 28px;
        }

        /* ===== COVER PAGE ===== */
        .cover-page {
            text-align: center;
            page-break-after: always;
            min-height: 9in;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .cover-logo {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 30pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a2332;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .cover-logo .accent {
            color: #c9a961;
        }

        .cover-tagline {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #888;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .cover-label {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #c9a961;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .cover-title {
            font-size: 24pt;
            color: #1a2332;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            max-width: 6in;
        }

        .cover-subtitle {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 11pt;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 80px;
            max-width: 5in;
        }

        .cover-meta {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 2;
        }

        .cover-meta strong {
            color: #1a2332;
        }

        .cover-divider {
            width: 60px;
            height: 3px;
            background: #c9a961;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
        }

        /* ===== SECTION HEADINGS ===== */
        h1 {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16pt;
            color: #1a2332;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #c9a961;
            padding-bottom: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 12pt;
            color: #1a2332;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        h3 {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 10.5pt;
            color: #555;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        ul, ol {
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            padding-left: 24px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        /* ===== TABLES ===== */
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        th {
            background: #1a2332;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        td {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        tr:nth-child(even) td {
            background: #f8f9fb;
        }

        /* ===== PRICING TABLE ===== */
        .pricing-total td {
            border-top: 2px solid #1a2332;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }

        .pricing-total .amount {
            text-align: right;
            color: #1a2332;
        }

        .right-align {
            text-align: right;
        }

        /* ===== CALL-OUT BOX ===== */
        .callout {
            background: #f4f1ea;
            border-left: 4px solid #c9a961;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #444;
        }

        /* ===== SIGNATURE BLOCK ===== */
        .signature-block {
            page-break-inside: avoid;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .sig-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .sig-col {
            width: 45%;
        }

        .sig-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            padding-top: 8px;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #666;
        }

        .sig-line strong {
            color: #1a2332;
            display: block;
            font-size: 10pt;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        /* ===== UTILITY ===== */
        .page-break {
            page-break-before: always;
        }

        .no-print {
            position: fixed;
            top: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            background: #1a2332;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 11px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            z-index: 9999;
        }

        /* ===== PRINT ===== */
        @media print {
            .no-print { display: none !important; }
            body { -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; }
            .cover-page { page-break-after: always; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <button class="no-print" onclick="window.print()">🖨️ Print / Save as PDF</button>

    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <!--               COVER PAGE                       -->
    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <div class="cover-page">
        <div class="cover-logo">NewSouth<span class="accent">Technologies</span></div>
        <div class="cover-tagline">Legacy Modernization · Governed Agility · Cybersecurity · AI Governance</div>
        <div class="cover-divider"></div>
        <div class="cover-label">PROPOSAL</div>
        <div class="cover-title">[Proposal Title — e.g., Legacy System Modernization &amp; Cybersecurity Assessment]</div>
        <div class="cover-subtitle">Prepared for [Client Organization Name]</div>
        <div class="cover-meta">
            <strong>Prepared by:</strong> NewSouth Technologies<br>
            <strong>Date:</strong> July 19, 2026<br>
            <strong>Valid through:</strong> [Expiration Date — 30 or 60 days]<br>
            <strong>Contact:</strong> Eugene Nkomba, Co-Managing Partner<br>
            <strong>Phone:</strong> [PHONE] &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Email:</strong> [EMAIL]<br>
            <strong>Website:</strong> www.newsouthtechnologies.com
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <!--           EXECUTIVE SUMMARY                    -->
    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <div class="page-header">
        <span class="ph-left">NewSouth Technologies</span>
        <span>Proposal — [Client Name]</span>
    </div>

    <h1>1. Executive Summary</h1>

    <p>Thank you for the opportunity to present this proposal. NewSouth Technologies specializes in helping organizations navigate the intersection of legacy modernization, cybersecurity, and governed agility — ensuring that mission-critical systems are secure, compliant, and positioned for future growth.</p>

    <p>This proposal outlines our recommended approach to [briefly describe engagement], the scope of work, timeline, and investment. We are confident that our methodology, grounded in proven frameworks such as [CMMC 2.0 / FedRAMP / SAFe / Scrum@Scale], will deliver measurable results aligned with your strategic objectives.</p>

    <div class="callout">
        <strong>Key Outcome:</strong> [One-sentence statement of the primary value/outcome the client will achieve.]
    </div>

    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <!--           CLIENT CHALLENGES                    -->
    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <h1>2. Understanding of Your Needs</h1>

    <p>Based on our preliminary discussions, we understand that [Client Organization] is currently facing:</p>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Challenge 1:</strong> [Description]</li>
        <li><strong>Challenge 2:</strong> [Description]</li>
        <li><strong>Challenge 3:</strong> [Description]</li>
    </ul>

    <p>These challenges are compounded by [additional context — regulatory pressure, budget constraints, talent gaps, etc.]. Our proposed engagement directly addresses each of these areas.</p>

    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <!--           PROPOSED APPROACH                    -->
    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <div class="page-header">
        <span class="ph-left">NewSouth Technologies</span>
        <span>Proposal — [Client Name]</span>
    </div>

    <h1>3. Proposed Approach &amp; Methodology</h1>

    <p>Our engagement follows a governed agile delivery model that balances structure with adaptability. We employ [describe methodology — Scrum, SAFe, custom governed agile framework] to ensure transparency, traceability, and continuous value delivery.</p>

    <h2>Phase 1: Discovery &amp; Assessment</h2>
    <p>[Description of discovery activities — stakeholder interviews, system inventory, gap analysis, risk assessment.]</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Stakeholder workshops and requirements gathering</li>
        <li>Current-state system and process documentation</li>
        <li>Gap analysis against [applicable framework]</li>
        <li>Risk and compliance assessment</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Phase 2: Strategy &amp; Roadmap</h2>
    <p>[Description of strategic planning activities — architecture recommendations, prioritization, roadmap development.]</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Target-state architecture definition</li>
        <li>Prioritized initiative backlog</li>
        <li>Implementation roadmap with milestones</li>
        <li>Resource and budget recommendations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Phase 3: Implementation &amp; Delivery</h2>
    <p>[Description of execution — sprint-based delivery, continuous integration, security validation.]</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Agile sprint execution with bi-weekly demos</li>
        <li>DevSecOps pipeline integration</li>
        <li>Cybersecurity controls implementation</li>
        <li>Continuous testing and compliance validation</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Phase 4: Transition &amp; Knowledge Transfer</h2>
    <p>[Description of handover — documentation, training, operational readiness.]</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Comprehensive documentation package</li>
        <li>Team training and enablement sessions</li>
        <li>Operational runbooks and procedures</li>
        <li>30-day post-implementation support</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <!--              SCOPE OF WORK                     -->
    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <div class="page-header">
        <span class="ph-left">NewSouth Technologies</span>
        <span>Proposal — [Client Name]</span>
    </div>

    <h1>4. Scope of Work</h1>

    <p>The following table outlines the specific deliverables for this engagement:</p>

    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th style="width: 25%;">Deliverable</th>
                <th style="width: 45%;">Description</th>
                <th style="width: 15%;">Phase</th>
                <th style="width: 15%;">Timeline</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>Assessment Report</td>
                <td>Comprehensive analysis of current systems, gaps, and risks</td>
                <td>Phase 1</td>
                <td>Weeks 1–3</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Strategic Roadmap</td>
                <td>Prioritized roadmap with architecture recommendations</td>
                <td>Phase 2</td>
                <td>Weeks 4–5</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Implementation Sprint(s)</td>
                <td>Execution of prioritized backlog items per agreed scope</td>
                <td>Phase 3</td>
                <td>Weeks 6–[N]</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Documentation Package</td>
                <td>Technical docs, runbooks, training materials</td>
                <td>Phase 4</td>
                <td>Final 2 weeks</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>4.1 Out of Scope</h2>
    <p>The following items are not included in this proposal but can be addressed under a separate engagement:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>[Item 1]</li>
        <li>[Item 2]</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <!--              TIMELINE                          -->
    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <h1>5. Timeline &amp; Milestones</h1>

    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th style="width: 25%;">Milestone</th>
                <th style="width: 20%;">Target Date</th>
                <th style="width: 55%;">Key Activities</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>Kickoff</td>
                <td>[Date]</td>
                <td>Project kickoff meeting, stakeholder alignment, access provisioning</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Assessment Complete</td>
                <td>[Date]</td>
                <td>Discovery findings presented, risk register delivered</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Roadmap Approved</td>
                <td>[Date]</td>
                <td>Strategic roadmap reviewed and approved by steering committee</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Implementation Complete</td>
                <td>[Date]</td>
                <td>All sprint deliverables accepted and validated</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Project Closeout</td>
                <td>[Date]</td>
                <td>Knowledge transfer, documentation handover, closeout report</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <!--              INVESTMENT                        -->
    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <div class="page-header">
        <span class="ph-left">NewSouth Technologies</span>
        <span>Proposal — [Client Name]</span>
    </div>

    <h1>6. Investment</h1>

    <p>The following table summarizes the proposed investment for this engagement. All amounts are in USD.</p>

    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th style="width: 35%;">Item</th>
                <th style="width: 15%;" class="right-align">Qty</th>
                <th style="width: 20%;" class="right-align">Rate</th>
                <th style="width: 30%;" class="right-align">Amount</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>Phase 1 — Discovery &amp; Assessment</td>
                <td class="right-align">[Hours]</td>
                <td class="right-align">$[Rate]/hr</td>
                <td class="right-align">$[Amount]</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Phase 2 — Strategy &amp; Roadmap</td>
                <td class="right-align">[Hours]</td>
                <td class="right-align">$[Rate]/hr</td>
                <td class="right-align">$[Amount]</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Phase 3 — Implementation</td>
                <td class="right-align">[Hours]</td>
                <td class="right-align">$[Rate]/hr</td>
                <td class="right-align">$[Amount]</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Phase 4 — Transition &amp; KT</td>
                <td class="right-align">[Hours]</td>
                <td class="right-align">$[Rate]/hr</td>
                <td class="right-align">$[Amount]</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="pricing-total">
                <td colspan="3">Total Investment</td>
                <td class="amount">$[TOTAL]</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>6.1 Payment Terms</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Payment Schedule:</strong> 30% upon signing, 40% at midpoint milestone, 30% upon project closeout</li>
        <li><strong>Invoicing:</strong> Net 15 from invoice date</li>
        <li><strong>Travel:</strong> Any travel expenses will be pre-approved and billed at cost</li>
        <li><strong>Validity:</strong> This proposal is valid for 30 days from the date above</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="callout">
        <strong>Value Assurance:</strong> All deliverables are backed by our quality guarantee. If any deliverable does not meet the acceptance criteria defined in the SOW, we will revise it at no additional cost.
    </div>

    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <!--           WHY NEWSOUTH                         -->
    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <h1>7. Why NewSouth Technologies</h1>

    <p>NewSouth Technologies brings a rare combination of deep technical expertise and executive-level consulting experience. Our team holds industry-leading credentials including:</p>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Cybersecurity &amp; Audit:</strong> CISA, CISM, CRISC</li>
        <li><strong>Project &amp; Agile Delivery:</strong> PMP, PMI-ACP, PSM III</li>
        <li><strong>Executive Coaching:</strong> ICF PCC, CPCC</li>
        <li><strong>Governance Frameworks:</strong> CMMC 2.0, FedRAMP, OMB circulars</li>
    </ul>

    <p>We understand that technology modernization is fundamentally an organizational change challenge. Our governed agility framework ensures that compliance, security, and innovation move forward together — not in tension.</p>

    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <!--           TERMS & CONDITIONS                   -->
    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <h1>8. Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>

    <h2>8.1 Confidentiality</h2>
    <p>Both parties agree to maintain confidentiality of all proprietary information shared during this engagement. A Mutual Non-Disclosure Agreement shall be executed prior to the commencement of work.</p>

    <h2>8.2 Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>All custom deliverables created specifically for [Client Organization] shall become the property of [Client Organization] upon full payment. NewSouth Technologies retains ownership of pre-existing methodologies, frameworks, and tools used in the delivery of services.</p>

    <h2>8.3 Change Management</h2>
    <p>Any changes to the scope of work will be documented in a written Change Order and signed by authorized representatives of both parties before work commences.</p>

    <h2>8.4 Termination</h2>
    <p>Either party may terminate this engagement with 30 days written notice. Fees for work completed up to the termination date shall be invoiced and paid per the payment terms above.</p>

    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <!--           ACCEPTANCE & SIGNATURES              -->
    <!-- ============================================= -->
    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <div class="page-header">
        <span class="ph-left">NewSouth Technologies</span>
        <span>Proposal — [Client Name]</span>
    </div>

    <h1>9. Acceptance</h1>

    <p>By signing below, the authorized representatives of both parties indicate their agreement to the terms outlined in this proposal and authorize the commencement of the engagement described herein.</p>

    <div class="signature-block">
        <div class="sig-row">
            <div class="sig-col">
                <div style="height: 60px;"></div>
                <div class="sig-line">
                    <strong>Eugene Nkomba</strong>
                    Co-Managing Partner<br>
                    NewSouth Technologies<br>
                    Date: _______________
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-col">
                <div style="height: 60px;"></div>
                <div class="sig-line">
                    <strong>[Client Signatory Name]</strong>
                    [Title]<br>
                    [Client Organization]<br>
                    Date: _______________
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 60px; text-align: center;">
        <p style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt; color: #999;">
            NewSouth Technologies | [ADDRESS] | [PHONE] | www.newsouthtechnologies.com<br>
            This proposal is confidential and prepared exclusively for [Client Organization].
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="page-footer">
        NewSouth Technologies — Confidential Proposal &nbsp;|&nbsp; Page generated July 19, 2026
    </div>

</body>
</html>